name: NetBricks
body:
NetBricks is a [Rust](https://rust-lang.org/) and [DPDK](https://dpdk.org) based NF platform. This is the initial source code release, and the code has inline comments and tests. We will be adding more to this site over time.

### Contact
If you need help, please e-mail [Aurojit Panda](https://cs.berkeley.edu/~apanda).
